      <h>Participation Guide</h>
      <p>
        This Participation Guide aims to help you gain the maximum 
        <a href="benefits">benefit from participating</a> in Online Groups.
      </p>
      <p>
        Often you want to 
        <a href="keep_track">keep track of conversations</a> in online 
        groups, without reading every post. At other times, you wish to
        <a href="follow_closely">follow a conversation closely</a>, or to
        <a href="contribute">contribute to a conversation</a>. This guide 
        explains different ways to do these things, and answers 
        <a href="faqs">frequently asked questions</a>.
      </p>
      <section id="help-participation-guide-contents">
        <h>Contents</h>
        <nl>
          <li href="benefits">Benefits of Online Participation</li>
