          <li href="follow_closely">Following Conversations Closely</li>
          <li href="contribute">Contributing to Conversations</li>
          <li href="faqs">Frequently Asked Questions</li>
        </nl>
      </section>
      <p>
        Please provide 
        <a href="mailto:support@onlinegroups.net">feedback to OnlineGroups.Net</a>
        about this Participation Guide, and your experience with this Online 
        Groups site.
      </p>  
